          <p>TITLE XII
ADOPTION OF CHILDREN
CHAPTER 1.  PRELIMINARY PROVISIONS; DEFINITIONS
Art. 1167.  Purpose
The purpose of this Title is to promote the permanent placement of available children into suitable homes through the procedures described herein.</p>
